  "story": {
    "text": {
      "en": "It started as a bug report — CRM hosts showing the same listing twice. By afternoon the fix had grown into a memory for the cockpit: every status change, note and follow-up lands in an append-only host_activity_events log, and a live_contact overlay shows rep marks instantly instead of after the hourly matview bake. Meanwhile, Florida listings — Airbnb and Furnished Finder both — kicked off a state-wide re-scrape.",
      "fr": "Tout a commencé par un bug — des hôtes du CRM affichant deux fois la même annonce. En après-midi, le correctif était devenu la mémoire du cockpit : chaque statut, note et suivi s'inscrit au journal host_activity_events, et l'overlay live_contact affiche les marques des reps sans attendre la matview horaire. En parallèle, les annonces de Floride — Airbnb et Furnished Finder — ont lancé un re-scrape complet."
    }
  },
